<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.3.6">
<l>eṭṭaṉaip poḻutā kilumeṉ ṟumeṉ maṉattaka lātiruk kumpukaḻ</l>
<l>taṭṭalartta poṉṉē yalarkōṅkiṉ tāḻpoḻil tirumā liruñcō laiyaṅ</l>
<l>kaṭṭiyai karumpīṉṟa viṉcāṟṟaik kātalālma ṟaināṉ kumuṉṉō tiya</l>
<l>paṭṭaṉaipa ravait tuyilēṟṟai yeṉpaṇ paṉaiyaṉṟip pāṭal ceyyēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without the jaggery mound of Tirumāliruñcōlai with low-hanging groves</l>
<l rend="indent">of silk-cotton trees with gold-like blossoms, blooming wide,</l>
<l>Whose fame has never left my mind, even if it is for a scintilla</l>
<l rend="indent">of a second’s time,</l>
<l>The sweet juice that sugarcane yields, the scholar who previously chanted</l>
<l rend="indent">the four Vedas with love,</l>
<l>The bull that sleeps in the sea, my [lord] of such qualities,</l>
<l rend="indent">I do not create songs.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
